You just want to watch, that's all.

00:21:28.720 --> 00:21:29.720
Gradually you'll grow.

00:21:29.720 --> 00:21:31.740
You see, this is the system Zen.

00:21:31.740 --> 00:21:36.820
Try to do it, but it was such a thing, you
know, that time, they were no such nice people

00:21:36.820 --> 00:21:37.820
like you, perhaps.

00:21:37.820 --> 00:21:42.340
So he had to use other methods to make people
go beyond the thought.

00:21:42.340 --> 00:21:46.260
For example, I was telling just now about
the tea ceremony.

00:21:46.260 --> 00:21:56.690
For tea ceremony, he would take a bowl of,
say, freak, like a freak.

00:21:56.690 --> 00:22:00.999
Freak, you understand the freak?

