Freak is a thing which comes out by nature
naturally in the cooking.

00:22:09.190 --> 00:22:16.970
When it is fried it becomes very funny type;
that is the freak.

00:22:16.970 --> 00:22:21.580
It's not regular.

00:22:21.580 --> 00:22:25.860
It's only one piece or something.

00:22:25.860 --> 00:22:28.270
Somebody who's Japanese here, who's come from
Japan?

00:22:28.270 --> 00:22:29.270
You?

00:22:29.270 --> 00:22:32.489
You people, they like, that's why freak very
much, you see.

00:22:32.489 --> 00:22:41.779
So, what he said that it is... , you take
the bowl in your hand for tea ceremony, that's

00:22:41.779 --> 00:22:43.580
the best.

00:22:43.580 --> 00:22:51.479
So first of all, you sit in a garden, with
natural trees and natural fibers of the wood

00:22:51.479 --> 00:22:53.340
and all that, sitting down.

00:22:53.340 --> 00:23:00.009
Now you start watching that thing, three times
sitting like this and three times like that.

00:23:00.009 --> 00:23:04.240
And don't think, that's the point, don't think.

00:23:04.240 --> 00:23:11.409
And then you take that tea; the tea is so
sour, so bitter, take quinine raised to the

00:23:11.409 --> 00:23:14.600
power of hundred and eight.

00:23:14.600 --> 00:23:22.649
Once you take that, you become absolutely
thoughtless; that's one.

00:23:22.649 --> 00:23:28.909
Then they give you a sweet; this sweet is
also sweetness, sugar raised to the power

00:23:28.909 --> 00:23:30.549
of hundred and eight.

00:23:30.549 --> 00:23:36.679
You just can't eat it, so you went from one
extreme to another extreme; again you become

00:23:36.679 --> 00:23:39.169
like that, you see, it's like standing.

00:23:39.169 --> 00:23:43.879
They put this side and that side and suddenly
it works out.

00:23:43.879 --> 00:23:49.549
But it's meant for people who already have
got Realization, not for people who have not

00:23:49.549 --> 00:23:50.549
got.

00:23:50.549 --> 00:23:54.100
That's why still they're studying Zen, you
know, this tea ceremony.

00:23:54.100 --> 00:24:02.259
When we went to Japan, you see, in one hotel,
they had arranged this tea ceremony and some

00:24:02.259 --> 00:24:06.470
Americans, they said one couple has to come,
they were fighting, "I'll go, I'll go."

00:24:06.470 --> 00:24:09.639
We have had the experience, so we were keeping
quiet, to see what's going to happen.

00:24:09.639 --> 00:24:14.729
And one couple came forward and knew they
were very jealous of them.

00:24:14.729 --> 00:24:19.909
They sat on the stage and then they brought
the tea; they make it with a very care and

00:24:19.909 --> 00:24:22.139
all that and gave it to the wife.

00:24:22.139 --> 00:24:28.700
She drank it and she was stunned, and then
they gave it to the husband.

00:24:28.700 --> 00:24:33.190
Her husband, you know, American after all,
he got so angry he threw the bowl.

00:24:33.190 --> 00:24:34.789
He said, "Damn it!

00:24:34.789 --> 00:24:38.049
You took so much money from us and what are
you giving us?"

00:24:38.049 --> 00:24:43.210
He gave all kinds of American abuses to them
and they came away and everybody started beating

00:24:43.210 --> 00:24:46.399
the people who had put up the show.

00:24:46.399 --> 00:24:51.220
So this is meant for people who really want
to go very deep.

00:24:51.220 --> 00:24:59.200
In Zen we also made a big courtyard filled
with sand, with some sort of designs in the

00:24:59.200 --> 00:25:03.419
sand and they put some stones in it.

00:25:03.419 --> 00:25:09.440
You are supposed to sit on the edge of that
and to look at it without thinking.

00:25:09.440 --> 00:25:14.889
But normally people start comparing, "It looks
like ships, it looks like this, it looks like..."

00:25:14.889 --> 00:25:17.700
No, you have to just look at it without thinking.

00:25:17.700 --> 00:25:22.309
There're many such things he did but nothing
worked out with them.

00:25:22.309 --> 00:25:29.090
There were only twenty-six people who got
Realization in the Zen system in the Sixth

00:25:29.090 --> 00:25:30.510
Century.

00:25:30.510 --> 00:25:35.869
From the Sixth Century to the Twelfth Century
and after that nobody got Realization.

00:25:35.869 --> 00:25:39.609
But there were very few and that's why they
don't understand Zen at all.

00:25:39.609 --> 00:25:45.070
You see, people write Zen because it's very
deep and they don't understand; so that's

00:25:45.070 --> 00:25:46.070
what it is.

