Now Sahaja Yoga is understood, can be understood
by normally educated person, by even uneducated

00:25:53.710 --> 00:25:54.710
people.

00:25:54.710 --> 00:25:57.989
And this happens because actualization takes
place.

00:25:57.989 --> 00:27:27.669
Your Kundalini takes an actual ascent.

00:27:27.669 --> 00:27:33.909
Now in Sahaja Yoga when people come in, there're
different categories of people also.

00:27:33.909 --> 00:27:42.849
Some of them come because they think they
can get good health; once they get good health

00:27:42.849 --> 00:27:43.999
they disappear.

