Then they again get some trouble, they come
back, just for good health.

00:27:48.419 --> 00:27:52.539
So you can't help, they have very limited
desires.

00:27:52.539 --> 00:27:58.019
Then some people come in Sahaja Yoga for throwing
their weight around, you see, showing off

00:27:58.019 --> 00:28:04.219
