00:28:10.129 --> 00:28:14.789
And they try to do it against the leader,
against this, "This is wrong with him, that

00:28:14.789 --> 00:28:16.859
is wrong with him," and all kinds of things.

00:28:16.859 --> 00:28:23.159
Thirdly people come but they don't come regularly
to Sahaja Yoga, they do not come regularly

00:28:23.159 --> 00:28:24.269
to the center.

00:28:24.269 --> 00:28:27.349
They just keep aloof and after some time they're
lost.

00:28:27.349 --> 00:28:32.029
They again get some diseases or trouble, then
they come back.

00:28:32.029 --> 00:28:37.279
So it's a religious duty of all of you to
come to the collective, one thing.

00:28:37.279 --> 00:28:45.049
The second one is to meditate everyday in
the night before sleeping on your mind.

00:28:45.049 --> 00:28:49.909
Everywhere you go you should be in a meditative
condition, in the sense, you should ask your

00:28:49.909 --> 00:28:52.809
mind what is it thinking.

00:28:52.809 --> 00:29:00.720
All should come to collective every time they
have a program wherever it is.

