So I've talked about God Realization in My
last speech in this thing, so you better listen

00:33:32.539 --> 00:33:47.499
to that lecture of Mine, for this puja, for
the Shiv Puja.

00:33:47.499 --> 00:33:53.700
So one should not even have ambitions, when
you have become a part and parcel of the whole,

00:33:53.700 --> 00:33:57.309
when you have become the ocean, what is there
to be ambitious?

00:33:57.309 --> 00:33:58.899
It's all individuality.

00:33:58.899 --> 00:34:17.050
You have 
to be a satisfied soul and I would say about

00:34:17.050 --> 00:34:23.210
Myself that I have to buy for My children,
for My husband, this thing, that thing, but

00:34:23.210 --> 00:34:42.929
I never buy anything for Myself, very difficult,
very difficult to buy something for Myself.

00:34:42.929 --> 00:34:47.310
And somebody says that, "Mother please what
will you have?"

00:34:47.310 --> 00:34:54.070
