I asked My daughter, "You make all kinds of
things for your father, what about Me?"

00:35:03.980 --> 00:35:16.000
So she said, "You don't like something in
particular, what to make for you, you tell

00:35:16.000 --> 00:35:20.790
us."

00:35:20.790 --> 00:35:25.130
All these attachments some people have, got
attachments to clothes, you see, "What I'll

00:35:25.130 --> 00:35:28.310
wear tomorrow, I'll wear day after tomorrow,"
like that.

00:35:28.310 --> 00:35:40.730
But so spontaneously whatever 
is available you can wear.

