And some worried about their past, you see,
"I'd a bad childhood," this, that, and they

00:35:45.610 --> 00:35:51.730
write about their parents; it's all nonsense,
forget it, you be in the present.

00:35:51.730 --> 00:36:08.350
Now you are no more a seed, you have to grow.

00:36:08.350 --> 00:36:15.910
That is something one has to understand in
life; that if you have to grow ourselves then

00:36:15.910 --> 00:36:24.220
what we have to see within ourself what lies,
whether that is doing wrong.

00:36:24.220 --> 00:36:35.870
That is something missing.

00:36:35.870 --> 00:36:44.710
Best is to see the good points of others,
not the bad points.

00:36:44.710 --> 00:36:52.710
By that you will gradually develop more good
points within yourself.

00:36:52.710 --> 00:37:01.870
Competition should be in good points.

00:37:01.870 --> 00:37:11.250
So on one side you have to achieve your self-Realization
in a way that you put yourself beyond the

00:37:11.250 --> 00:37:18.360
mind, one way, through meditation.

00:37:18.360 --> 00:37:32.540
And the second way is to give Realizations
to others.

00:37:32.540 --> 00:37:37.050
And must attend collective meditation, very
important.

00:37:37.050 --> 00:37:44.970
You have to be active in it.

00:37:44.970 --> 00:37:50.130
If you are not active in Sahaja Yoga then
you lose your vibrations gradually because

00:37:50.130 --> 00:38:05.400
Divine thinks, "What's the use of giving to
this hopeless case any vibrations."

00:38:05.400 --> 00:38:11.890
So you have to work it out, understanding
that now you are chosen as the instrument

00:38:11.890 --> 00:38:14.320
of the Divine.

00:38:14.320 --> 00:38:25.090
It is not only for your health or for the
health of your family or for anything like

00:38:25.090 --> 00:38:26.090
that.

00:38:26.090 --> 00:38:29.300
But it is for the good of the others.

00:38:29.300 --> 00:38:41.370
That's how you'll all go very well.

00:38:41.370 --> 00:38:52.540
Now diffidence comes through your mind only;
mind only gives you diffidence.

00:38:52.540 --> 00:38:57.690
